text: Neilrex is a bounded rural locality in north-western New South Wales, Australia. A now-removed railway station on the Gwabegar railway line was located there between 1917 and 1974.Nielrex NSWrail.net, accessed 9 April 2010. Wheat silos and a siding remain in use. ==References== Category:Localities in New South Wales Category:Warrumbungle Shire
title: Neilrex, New South Wales
